naan rajavaga pogiren ( english : i am going to become a king ) is a 2013 tamil action film co-written and directed by prithvi rajkumar , assistant of vetrimaaran and writer of sathyaraj starrer lootty and 6.2 . the film features nakul , chandni and newcomer avani modi in the lead roles . the film opened average reviews and was an average grosser at the box office .